responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "FE7889F54BBA73A1EE6E93B0D43D1585", "The bible of the Divine Carnage! Then the Flayer is defeated this day, but he can always return in a new form. He and his Divine Carnage shall be a problem for us along this odyssey. We shall keep our senses on alert. We thank you. I am confident we shall cross paths once more.")
